# ============================================================================
# Cursor Indexing Additional Exclusions (Not in .gitignore)
# ============================================================================
# Purpose: Patterns that should be excluded from Cursor indexing but are NOT
# in .gitignore (i.e., files that ARE committed to Git).
#
# This file is combined with .gitignore to generate .cursorindexingignore
# To regenerate: make cursor-indexing-ignore
#
# Single Source of Truth (SST) Architecture:
# - .gitignore                      → Master for Git exclusions
# - .cursorindexingignore.additions → Master for Cursor-only exclusions
# - .cursorindexingignore           → Generated (DO NOT EDIT DIRECTLY)
# ============================================================================

# ============================================================================
# Binary Images (267 files: 91 PNG, 89 SVG, 87 JPG)
# ============================================================================
# Rationale: Committed for documentation but binary files aren't searchable
# and significantly slow indexing performance
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.gif
*.bmp
*.tiff
*.ico
*.svg
*.eps
*.webp
*.heic
*.heif

# ============================================================================
# Generated PDFs (302 files including main documents)
# ============================================================================
# Rationale: Committed to Git for distribution but shouldn't be indexed
# - Binary files (not searchable)
# - Large (HAFiscal.pdf = 1.0M, HAFiscal-Slides.pdf = 533K)
# - Frequently regenerated (forces re-indexing)
*.pdf
HAFiscal.pdf
HAFiscal-Slides.pdf
Figures/
Tables/
Subfiles/*.pdf

# ============================================================================
# Historical/Archive Directories (27 markdown files)
# ============================================================================
# Rationale: Historical content not relevant for current development
history/
Highlighted/

# ============================================================================
# Private Content Directories (130MB total)
# ============================================================================
# Rationale: Private notes, presentations, and reference materials
# May be committed but shouldn't be indexed for privacy and performance
*_private/
Private/
Notes_Private/
Presentations_private/
Related-Lit-private/
resources-private/
private-dev/

# ============================================================================
# LaTeX Package Dependencies (5.8MB, 43 packages)
# ============================================================================
# Rationale: External LaTeX packages stored locally for minimal installation
# These are dependencies, not project source code
@local/texlive/texmf-local/tex/latex/

